        {
            "title": "「高官樓后」謝小華復出做局長　曾申報擁18項物業9個車位　去年3,480萬買帝景峰四房",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YJtJbM_mra6J.JRS_G_TMw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/28hse_com_210/9163143c7eda7c136dba5f4e379ebd13\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E6%A8%93%E5%90%8E-%E8%AC%9D%E5%B0%8F%E8%8F%AF%E5%BE%A9%E5%87%BA%E5%81%9A%E5%B1%80%E9%95%B7-%E6%9B%BE%E7%94%B3%E5%A0%B1%E6%93%8118%E9%A0%85%E7%89%A9%E6%A5%AD9%E5%80%8B%E8%BB%8A%E4%BD%8D-%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B43-480%E8%90%AC%E8%B2%B7%E5%B8%9D%E6%99%AF%E5%B3%B0%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%BF-104535079.html",
